metadata.name: Heart Full of Love - Zach Gill
metadata.description:
Zach Gill - Piano, Vocals, Songwriting

Zach Gill is a multi-instrumentalist, singer/songwriter most known for his work with ALO and Jack Johnson. He’s performed for presidents, alongside rock stars, on television, and in historic venues throughout the world.

Everyone Orchestra’s Heart Full of Love is a 20th Anniversary Celebration produced by Matt Butler and Todd Kushnir. 

73 incredible artists participated in this project. Virtually conducted, digital files were sent back and forth and then overlaid, mixed and mastered to become a magnum opus for Everyone Orchestra - a true and wide-ranging celebration of creativity, collaboration, community, and improvisation. A fun and happy song meant to lift your hearts and spirits. In a time when hopefulness can be hard to come by, and the music industry is once again being wrought with cancellations and lost touring opportunities, our hope is to raise the vibration as much as we can by putting out this work, at this time.

Produced by  
Matt Butler & Todd Kushnir  
NFT Design, Editing, & Sound - KUSH  
c.2022
